serviceDescription.content:
SoMedia is a social media management platform that allows users to:

- Connect and manage social media accounts (Instagram, Facebook, Threads, YouTube, TikTok, X and others);
- Schedule, publish and manage content across multiple platforms;
- Track performance metrics and analytics;
- Create and manage custom short links;
- Store and organize digital media;
- Use artificial intelligence tools to assist in content creation.

The Service is provided "as is" and "as available". We do not guarantee that the Service will be uninterrupted, timely, secure or error-free.

